casebody.data:
No. 819,

Mise.

Haynes v. Rederi A/S Aladdin et al. Arthur J. Mandell for petitioner. Edward W. Watson for respondents. E. D. Vickery and Mayo J. Thompson for Texas Employers’ Insurance Association, intervenor below, on the briefs in opposition to the petition and to the motion. Robert Klonsky and Philip F. DiCostanzo for American Trial Lawyers Association, as amicus curiae, in support of the petition.

C. A. 5th Cir. Motion of American Trial Lawyers Association for leave to file brief, as amicus curiae, granted. Certiorari denied.
